description: AIDS Help, a non-profit community-based organization, provides case-managed health care, housing, food, counseling, referral, PrEP and nPEP referrals and support services for HIV-infected residents of Monroe County (the Florida Keys). The agency also conducts health education, HIV risk reduction and outreach programs aimed at reducing the impact of HIV infection throughout the County.\n\n###MON###
name: AIDS HELP, INC.
